name: Jeffrey Hull
what_you_do: Jeffrey Hull is an author, educator, and consultant with more than twenty years' experience partnering with C-suite executives on issues of high-performance leadership, change management, organizational strategy, structure, and culture.
who_you_serve: C-suite executives, next generation executives, entrepreneurs and senior business professionals
offering: Executive coaching, team coaching, and speaking events
social_proof: Author of Forbes Top Business Book 2019 'Flex', clinical instructor in psychology at Harvard Medical School, adjunct professor of leadership at New York University
business_focus: Helping leaders and organizations unlock their leadership potential and achieve high performance
service_provided: Executive coaching, team coaching, speaking events
